GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF NORTH CAROLINA
SESSION 2025
H 1
HOUSE BILL 880
Short Title: Aggie Academy Learning Lab/Funds. (Public)
Sponsors: Representatives Quick, Clark, Harrison, and Branson (Primary Sponsors).
For a complete list of sponsors, refer to the North Carolina General Assembly web site.
Referred to: Appropriations, if favorable, Rules, Calendar, and Operations of the House
April 10, 2025
1 A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
2 AN ACT TO APPROPRIATE ADDITIONAL FUNDS TO SUPPORT AGGIE ACADEMY, A
3 UNIVERSITY OF NORTH CAROLINA LABORATORY SCHOOL AT NORTH
4 CAROLINA AGRICULTURAL AND TECHNICAL STATE UNIVERSITY.
5 The General Assembly of North Carolina enacts:
6 SECTION 1. There is appropriated from the General Fund to the Board of Governors
7 of The University of North Carolina the sum of one million dollars ($1,000,000) in recurring
8 funds for the 2025-2026 fiscal year to be allocated to North Carolina Agricultural and Technical
9 State University to provide additional support for NC A&T Aggie Academy, a University of
10 North Carolina laboratory school established pursuant to Article 29A of Chapter 116 of the
11 General Statutes.
12 SECTION 2. This act becomes effective July 1, 2025.
